{
  "video_id": "IOABs1cOqDo",
  "title": "Don't fail fast -- fail mindfully | Leticia Gasca",
  "es": 0,
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 12280.0,
      "end_time": 15856.0,
      "text": "[This talk contains mature language Viewer discretion is advised]"
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 15880.0,
      "end_time": 20576.0,
      "text": "If we traveled back to the year 800 BC,"
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 20600.0,
      "end_time": 24416.0,
      "text": "in Greece, we would see that merchants whose businesses failed"
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 24440.0,
      "end_time": 28760.0,
      "text": "were forced to sit in the marketplace with a basket over their heads."
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 29800.0,
      "end_time": 31576.0,
      "text": "In premodern Italy,"
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 31600.0,
      "end_time": 34976.0,
      "text": "failed business owners, who had outstanding debts,"
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 35000.0,
      "end_time": 38775.0,
      "text": "were taken totally naked to the public square"
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 38800.0,
      "end_time": 42455.0,
      "text": "where they had to bang their butts against a special stone"
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 42480.0,
      "end_time": 44839.0,
      "text": "while a crowd jeered at them."
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 45960.0,
      "end_time": 48816.0,
      "text": "In the 17th century in France,"
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 48840.0,
      "end_time": 52656.0,
      "text": "failed business owners were taken to the center of the market,"
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 52680.0,
      "end_time": 56416.0,
      "text": "where the beginning of their bankruptcy was publicly announced."
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 56440.0,
      "end_time": 59696.0,
      "text": "And in order to avoid immediate imprisonment,"
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 59720.0,
      "end_time": 61775.0,
      "text": "they had to wear a green bonnet"
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 61800.0,
      "end_time": 65160.0,
      "text": "so that everyone knew they were a failure."
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 65840.0,
      "end_time": 69216.0,
      "text": "Of course, these are extreme examples."
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 69240.0,
      "end_time": 71295.0,
      "text": "But it is important to remember"
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 71320.0,
      "end_time": 74655.0,
      "text": "that when we excessively punish those who fail,"
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 74680.0,
      "end_time": 77816.0,
      "text": "we stifle innovation and business creation,"
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 77840.0,
      "end_time": 81400.0,
      "text": "the engines of economic growth in any country."
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 82480.0,
      "end_time": 88216.0,
      "text": "Time has passed, and today we don&#39;t publicly humiliate failed entrepreneurs."
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 88240.0,
      "end_time": 91440.0,
      "text": "And they don&#39;t broadcast their failures on social media."
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 92200.0,
      "end_time": 97656.0,
      "text": "In fact, I think that all of us can relate with the pain of failure."
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 97680.0,
      "end_time": 101960.0,
      "text": "But we don&#39;t share the details of those experiences."
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 101120.0,
      "end_time": 105456.0,
      "text": "And I totally get it, my friends, I have also been there."
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 105480.0,
      "end_time": 107136.0,
      "text": "I had a business that failed"
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 107160.0,
      "end_time": 110896.0,
      "text": "and sharing that story was incredibly hard."
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 110920.0,
      "end_time": 116296.0,
      "text": "In fact, it required seven years, a good dose of vulnerability"
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 116320.0,
      "end_time": 118390.0,
      "text": "and the company of my friends."
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 118960.0,
      "end_time": 120679.0,
      "text": "This is my failure story."
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 121440.0,
      "end_time": 126376.0,
      "text": "When I was in college, studying business, I met a group of indigenous women."
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 126400.0,
      "end_time": 131776.0,
      "text": "They lived in a poor rural community in the state of Puebla, in central Mexico."
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 131800.0,
      "end_time": 135960.0,
      "text": "They made beautiful handmade products."
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 135120.0,
      "end_time": 138560.0,
      "text": "And when I met them and I saw their work,"
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 138800.0,
      "end_time": 140800.0,
      "text": "I decided I wanted to help."
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 140840.0,
      "end_time": 144176.0,
      "text": "With some friends, I cofounded a social enterprise"
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 144200.0,
      "end_time": 148160.0,
      "text": "with the mission to help the women create an income stream"
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 148400.0,
      "end_time": 150280.0,
      "text": "and improve their quality of life."
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 151800.0,
      "end_time": 153856.0,
      "text": "We did everything by the book,"
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 153880.0,
      "end_time": 156496.0,
      "text": "as we had learned in business school."
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 156520.0,
      "end_time": 157936.0,
      "text": "We got investors,"
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 157960.0,
      "end_time": 163616.0,
      "text": "we spent a lot of time building the business and training the women."
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 163640.0,
      "end_time": 167416.0,
      "text": "But soon we realized we were novices."
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 167440.0,
      "end_time": 170696.0,
      "text": "The handmade products were not selling,"
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 170720.0,
      "end_time": 175416.0,
      "text": "and the financial plan we had made was totally unrealistic."
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 175440.0,
      "end_time": 179696.0,
      "text": "In fact, we worked for years without a salary,"
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 179720.0,
      "end_time": 182560.0,
      "text": "hoping that a miracle would happen,"
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 182800.0,
      "end_time": 184776.0,
      "text": "that magically a great buyer would arrive"
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 184800.0,
      "end_time": 187120.0,
      "text": "and she would make the business profitable."
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 187920.0,
      "end_time": 189959.0,
      "text": "But that miracle never happened."
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 190920.0,
      "end_time": 193736.0,
      "text": "In the end, we had to close the business,"
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 193760.0,
      "end_time": 196400.0,
      "text": "and that broke my heart."
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 197000.0,
      "end_time": 200296.0,
      "text": "I started everything to create a positive impact"
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 200320.0,
      "end_time": 202416.0,
      "text": "on the life of the artisans."
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 202440.0,
      "end_time": 204760.0,
      "text": "And I felt that I have done the opposite."
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 205720.0,
      "end_time": 208960.0,
      "text": "I felt so guilty"
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 208120.0,
      "end_time": 210416.0,
      "text": "that I decided to hide this failure"
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 210440.0,
      "end_time": 214896.0,
      "text": "from my conversations and my resume for years."
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 214920.0,
      "end_time": 217375.0,
      "text": "I didn&#39;t know other failed entrepreneurs,"
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 217400.0,
      "end_time": 220760.0,
      "text": "and I thought I was the only loser in the world."
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 222320.0,
      "end_time": 226775.0,
      "text": "One night, seven years later, I was out with some friends"
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 226800.0,
      "end_time": 230296.0,
      "text": "and we were talking about the life of the entrepreneur."
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 230320.0,
      "end_time": 233680.0,
      "text": "And of course, the issue of failure came out."
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 234280.0,
      "end_time": 238896.0,
      "text": "I decided to confess to my friends the story of my failed business."
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 238920.0,
      "end_time": 241655.0,
      "text": "And they shared similar stories."
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 241680.0,
      "end_time": 246976.0,
      "text": "In that moment, a thought became really clear in my mind:"
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 247000.0,
      "end_time": 249216.0,
      "text": "all of my friends were failures."
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 249240.0,
      "end_time": 251296.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 251320.0,
      "end_time": 254335.0,
      "text": "Being more serious, that night I realized"
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 254360.0,
      "end_time": 258456.0,
      "text": "that A: I wasn&#39;t the only loser in the world,"
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 258480.00000000003,
      "end_time": 262496.0,
      "text": "and B: we all have hidden failures."
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 262520.0,
      "end_time": 264359.0,
      "text": "Please tell me if that is not true."
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 266320.0,
      "end_time": 269856.0,
      "text": "That night was like an exorcism for me."
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 269880.0,
      "end_time": 275416.0,
      "text": "I realized that sharing your failures makes you stronger, not weaker."
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 275440.0,
      "end_time": 277776.0,
      "text": "And being open to my vulnerability"
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 277800.0,
      "end_time": 282176.0,
      "text": "helped me connect with others in a deeper and more meaningful way"
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 282200.0,
      "end_time": 286200.0,
      "text": "and embrace life lessons I wouldn&#39;t have learned previously."
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 287200.0,
      "end_time": 289296.0,
      "text": "As a consequence of this experience"
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 289320.0,
      "end_time": 292656.0,
      "text": "of sharing stories of businesses that didn&#39;t work,"
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 292680.0,
      "end_time": 295960.0,
      "text": "we decided to create a platform of events"
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 295120.0,
      "end_time": 298176.0,
      "text": "to help others share their failure stories."
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 298200.0,
      "end_time": 300520.0,
      "text": "And we called it Fuckup Nights."
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 301560.0,
      "end_time": 305960.0,
      "text": "Years later, we also created a research center"
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 305120.0,
      "end_time": 306936.0,
      "text": "devoted to the story of failure"
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 306960.0,
      "end_time": 310936.0,
      "text": "and its implications on business, people and society"
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 310960.0,
      "end_time": 315640.0,
      "text": "and as we love cool names, we called it the Failure Institute."
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 316840.0,
      "end_time": 319496.0,
      "text": "It has been surprising to see"
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 319520.0,
      "end_time": 322335.0,
      "text": "that when an entrepreneur stands on a stage"
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 322360.0,
      "end_time": 324296.0,
      "text": "and shares a story of failure,"
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 324320.0,
      "end_time": 327496.0,
      "text": "she can actually enjoy that experience."
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 327520.0,
      "end_time": 331536.0,
      "text": "It doesn&#39;t have to be a moment of shame and embarrassment,"
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 331560.0,
      "end_time": 333736.0,
      "text": "as it used to be in the past."
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 333760.0,
      "end_time": 336256.0,
      "text": "It is an opportunity to share lessons learned"
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 336280.0,
      "end_time": 338560.0,
      "text": "and build empathy."
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 338800.0,
      "end_time": 339575.0,
      "text": "We have also discovered"
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 339600.0,
      "end_time": 344696.0,
      "text": "that when the members of a team share their failures, magic happens."
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 344720.0,
      "end_time": 348760.0,
      "text": "Bonds grow stronger and collaboration becomes easier."
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 349600.0,
      "end_time": 351936.0,
      "text": "Through our events and research projects,"
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 351960.0,
      "end_time": 354616.0,
      "text": "we have found some interesting facts."
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 354640.0,
      "end_time": 358895.0,
      "text": "For instance, that men and women react in a different way"
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 358920.0,
      "end_time": 361336.0,
      "text": "after the failure of a business."
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 361360.0,
      "end_time": 364256.0,
      "text": "The most common reaction among men"
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 364280.0,
      "end_time": 368950.0,
      "text": "is to start a new business within one year of failure,"
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 368120.0,
      "end_time": 370256.0,
      "text": "but in a different sector,"
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 370280.0,
      "end_time": 373560.0,
      "text": "while women decide to look for a job"
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 373800.0,
      "end_time": 376176.0,
      "text": "and postpone the creation of a new business."
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 376200.0,
      "end_time": 378496.0,
      "text": "Our hypothesis is that this happens"
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 378520.0,
      "end_time": 382816.0,
      "text": "because women tend to suffer more from the impostor syndrome."
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 382840.0,
      "end_time": 387816.0,
      "text": "We feel that we need something else to be a good entrepreneur."
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 387840.0,
      "end_time": 393655.0,
      "text": "But I have seen that in many, many cases women have everything that&#39;s needed."
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 393680.0,
      "end_time": 395920.0,
      "text": "We just need to take the step."
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 396640.0,
      "end_time": 398216.0,
      "text": "And in the case of men,"
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 398240.0,
      "end_time": 402496.0,
      "text": "it is more common to see that they feel they have enough knowledge"
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 402520.0,
      "end_time": 407159.0,
      "text": "and just need to put it in practice in another place with better luck."
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 407920.0,
      "end_time": 410416.0,
      "text": "Another interesting finding has been"
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 410440.0,
      "end_time": 415000.0,
      "text": "that there are regional differences on how entrepreneurs cope with failure."
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 415720.0,
      "end_time": 418960.0,
      "text": "For instance, the most common reaction"
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 418120.0,
      "end_time": 421456.0,
      "text": "after the failure of a business in the American continent"
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 421480.0,
      "end_time": 423656.0,
      "text": "is to go back to school."
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 423680.0,
      "end_time": 428256.0,
      "text": "While in Europe, the most common reaction is to look for a therapist."
    },
    {
      "index": 121,
      "start_time": 428280.0,
      "end_time": 430895.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 122,
      "start_time": 430920.0,
      "end_time": 434936.0,
      "text": "We&#39;re not sure which is a better reaction after the failure of a business,"
    },
    {
      "index": 123,
      "start_time": 434960.0,
      "end_time": 439159.0,
      "text": "but this is something we will study in the future."
    },
    {
      "index": 124,
      "start_time": 440000.0,
      "end_time": 443960.0,
      "text": "Another interesting finding has been"
    },
    {
      "index": 125,
      "start_time": 443120.0,
      "end_time": 448776.0,
      "text": "the profound impact that public policy has on failed entrepreneurs."
    },
    {
      "index": 126,
      "start_time": 448800.0,
      "end_time": 451296.0,
      "text": "For instance, in my country, in Mexico,"
    },
    {
      "index": 127,
      "start_time": 451320.0,
      "end_time": 454616.0,
      "text": "the regulatory environment is so hard,"
    },
    {
      "index": 128,
      "start_time": 454640.0,
      "end_time": 459656.0,
      "text": "that closing a business can take you a lot of time and a lot of money."
    },
    {
      "index": 129,
      "start_time": 459680.0,
      "end_time": 461680.0,
      "text": "Let&#39;s begin with the money."
    },
    {
      "index": 130,
      "start_time": 462400.0,
      "end_time": 464335.0,
      "text": "In the best possible scenario,"
    },
    {
      "index": 131,
      "start_time": 464360.0,
      "end_time": 466976.0,
      "text": "meaning you don&#39;t have problems with partners,"
    },
    {
      "index": 132,
      "start_time": 467000.0,
      "end_time": 469696.0,
      "text": "providers, clients, employees,"
    },
    {
      "index": 133,
      "start_time": 469720.0,
      "end_time": 471776.0,
      "text": "in the best possible scenario,"
    },
    {
      "index": 134,
      "start_time": 471800.0,
      "end_time": 475976.0,
      "text": "officially closing a business will cost you 2,000 dollars."
    },
    {
      "index": 135,
      "start_time": 476000.0,
      "end_time": 478960.0,
      "text": "Which is a lot of money in Mexico."
    },
    {
      "index": 136,
      "start_time": 478120.0,
      "end_time": 480336.0,
      "text": "Someone who earns the minimum wage"
    },
    {
      "index": 137,
      "start_time": 480360.0,
      "end_time": 483840.0,
      "text": "would have to work for 15 months to save this amount."
    },
    {
      "index": 138,
      "start_time": 484560.0,
      "end_time": 487136.0,
      "text": "Now, let&#39;s talk about the time."
    },
    {
      "index": 139,
      "start_time": 487160.0,
      "end_time": 490376.0,
      "text": "As you may know, in most of the developing world,"
    },
    {
      "index": 140,
      "start_time": 490400.0,
      "end_time": 494400.0,
      "text": "the average life expectancy of a business is two years."
    },
    {
      "index": 141,
      "start_time": 495160.0,
      "end_time": 500800.0,
      "text": "In Mexico, the process of officially closing a business takes two years."
    },
    {
      "index": 142,
      "start_time": 501720.0,
      "end_time": 505376.0,
      "text": "What happens when the average life expectancy of a business"
    },
    {
      "index": 143,
      "start_time": 505400.0,
      "end_time": 510400.0,
      "text": "is so similar to the time it will take you to close it if it doesn&#39;t work?"
    },
    {
      "index": 144,
      "start_time": 511120.0,
      "end_time": 514176.0,
      "text": "Of course, this discourages business creation"
    },
    {
      "index": 145,
      "start_time": 514200.00000000006,
      "end_time": 516000.00000000006,
      "text": "and promotes informal economy."
    },
    {
      "index": 146,
      "start_time": 516840.00000000006,
      "end_time": 519416.00000000006,
      "text": "In fact, econometric research has proved"
    },
    {
      "index": 147,
      "start_time": 519440.00000000006,
      "end_time": 524936.0,
      "text": "that if the process of declaring bankruptcy takes less time and less money,"
    },
    {
      "index": 148,
      "start_time": 524960.0,
      "end_time": 527679.0,
      "text": "more new firms will enter the market."
    },
    {
      "index": 149,
      "start_time": 528480.0,
      "end_time": 531336.0,
      "text": "For this reason, in 2017,"
    },
    {
      "index": 150,
      "start_time": 531360.0,
      "end_time": 534775.0,
      "text": "we proposed a series of public policy recommendations"
    },
    {
      "index": 151,
      "start_time": 534799.0,
      "end_time": 539960.0,
      "text": "for the procedure of officially closing businesses in Mexico."
    },
    {
      "index": 152,
      "start_time": 539120.0,
      "end_time": 540776.0,
      "text": "For a whole year,"
    },
    {
      "index": 153,
      "start_time": 540800.0,
      "end_time": 544136.0,
      "text": "we worked with entrepreneurs from all over the country"
    },
    {
      "index": 154,
      "start_time": 544160.0,
      "end_time": 545616.0,
      "text": "and with Congress."
    },
    {
      "index": 155,
      "start_time": 545640.0,
      "end_time": 549120.0,
      "text": "And the good news is that we managed to help change the law."
    },
    {
      "index": 156,
      "start_time": 550240.0,
      "end_time": 551456.0,
      "text": "Yay!"
    },
    {
      "index": 157,
      "start_time": 551480.0,
      "end_time": 554496.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 158,
      "start_time": 554520.0,
      "end_time": 558216.0,
      "text": "The idea is that when the new regulation comes into force,"
    },
    {
      "index": 159,
      "start_time": 558240.0,
      "end_time": 563336.0,
      "text": "entrepreneurs will be able to close their businesses in an online procedure"
    },
    {
      "index": 160,
      "start_time": 563360.0,
      "end_time": 565800.0,
      "text": "that is faster and inexpensive."
    },
    {
      "index": 161,
      "start_time": 566760.0,
      "end_time": 568616.0,
      "text": "(Sighs)"
    },
    {
      "index": 162,
      "start_time": 568640.0,
      "end_time": 570856.0,
      "text": "On the night we invented Fuckup Nights,"
    },
    {
      "index": 163,
      "start_time": 570880.0,
      "end_time": 575360.0,
      "text": "we never imagined that the movement would grow this big."
    },
    {
      "index": 164,
      "start_time": 576160.0,
      "end_time": 578736.0,
      "text": "We are in 80 countries now."
    },
    {
      "index": 165,
      "start_time": 578760.0,
      "end_time": 581536.0,
      "text": "In that moment, our only intention"
    },
    {
      "index": 166,
      "start_time": 581560.0,
      "end_time": 584935.0,
      "text": "was to put the topic of failure on the table."
    },
    {
      "index": 167,
      "start_time": 584960.0,
      "end_time": 588656.0,
      "text": "To help our friends see that failure is something we must talk about."
    },
    {
      "index": 168,
      "start_time": 588680.0,
      "end_time": 593295.0,
      "text": "It is not a cause of humiliation, as it used to be in the past,"
    },
    {
      "index": 169,
      "start_time": 593320.0,
      "end_time": 596800.0,
      "text": "or a cause of celebration, as some people say."
    },
    {
      "index": 170,
      "start_time": 596920.0,
      "end_time": 599839.0,
      "text": "In fact, I want to confess something."
    },
    {
      "index": 171,
      "start_time": 600760.0,
      "end_time": 604976.0,
      "text": "Every time I listen to Silicon Valley types or students"
    },
    {
      "index": 172,
      "start_time": 605000.0,
      "end_time": 610640.0,
      "text": "bragging about failing fast and often like it&#39;s no big deal, I cringe."
    },
    {
      "index": 173,
      "start_time": 611480.0,
      "end_time": 616400.0,
      "text": "Because I think that there is a dark side on the mantra \"fail fast.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 174,
      "start_time": 617000.0,
      "end_time": 621336.0,
      "text": "Of course, failing fast is a great way to accelerate learning"
    },
    {
      "index": 175,
      "start_time": 621360.0,
      "end_time": 623216.0,
      "text": "and avoid wasting time."
    },
    {
      "index": 176,
      "start_time": 623240.0,
      "end_time": 626776.0,
      "text": "But I fear that when we present rapid failure"
    },
    {
      "index": 177,
      "start_time": 626800.0,
      "end_time": 629656.0,
      "text": "to entrepreneurs as their one and only option,"
    },
    {
      "index": 178,
      "start_time": 629680.0,
      "end_time": 632960.0,
      "text": "we might be promoting laziness."
    },
    {
      "index": 179,
      "start_time": 632120.0,
      "end_time": 635520.0,
      "text": "We might be promoting that entrepreneurs give up too easily."
    },
    {
      "index": 180,
      "start_time": 636280.0,
      "end_time": 639336.0,
      "text": "I also fear that the culture of rapid failure"
    },
    {
      "index": 181,
      "start_time": 639360.0,
      "end_time": 643176.0,
      "text": "could be minimizing the devastating consequences"
    },
    {
      "index": 182,
      "start_time": 643200.0,
      "end_time": 644840.0,
      "text": "of the failure of a business."
    },
    {
      "index": 183,
      "start_time": 645600.0,
      "end_time": 649960.0,
      "text": "For instance, when my social enterprise died,"
    },
    {
      "index": 184,
      "start_time": 649120.0,
      "end_time": 654616.0,
      "text": "the worst part was that I had to go back to the indigenous community"
    },
    {
      "index": 185,
      "start_time": 654640.0,
      "end_time": 657616.0,
      "text": "and tell the women that the business had failed"
    },
    {
      "index": 186,
      "start_time": 657640.0,
      "end_time": 659400.0,
      "text": "and it was my fault."
    },
    {
      "index": 187,
      "start_time": 660280.0,
      "end_time": 665256.0,
      "text": "For some people this could be seen like a great learning opportunity for me,"
    },
    {
      "index": 188,
      "start_time": 665280.0,
      "end_time": 668336.0,
      "text": "but the truth is that the closure of this business"
    },
    {
      "index": 189,
      "start_time": 668360.0,
      "end_time": 670920.0,
      "text": "represented much more than that."
    },
    {
      "index": 190,
      "start_time": 671520.0,
      "end_time": 674856.0,
      "text": "It meant that the women would stop receiving an income"
    },
    {
      "index": 191,
      "start_time": 674880.0,
      "end_time": 676600.0,
      "text": "that they really needed."
    },
    {
      "index": 192,
      "start_time": 677720.0,
      "end_time": 680976.0,
      "text": "For this reason, I want to propose something."
    },
    {
      "index": 193,
      "start_time": 681000.0,
      "end_time": 685960.0,
      "text": "I want to propose that just as we put aside the idea"
    },
    {
      "index": 194,
      "start_time": 685120.0,
      "end_time": 688336.0,
      "text": "of publicly humiliating failed entrepreneurs,"
    },
    {
      "index": 195,
      "start_time": 688360.0,
      "end_time": 694336.0,
      "text": "we must put aside the idea that failing fast is always the best."
    },
    {
      "index": 196,
      "start_time": 694360.0,
      "end_time": 697136.0,
      "text": "And I want to propose a new mantra:"
    },
    {
      "index": 197,
      "start_time": 697160.0,
      "end_time": 699496.0,
      "text": "fail mindfully."
    },
    {
      "index": 198,
      "start_time": 699520.0,
      "end_time": 703415.0,
      "text": "We must remember that businesses are made of people,"
    },
    {
      "index": 199,
      "start_time": 703440.0,
      "end_time": 706816.0,
      "text": "businesses are not entities that appear and disappear"
    },
    {
      "index": 200,
      "start_time": 706840.0,
      "end_time": 709536.0,
      "text": "magically without consequences."
    },
    {
      "index": 201,
      "start_time": 709560.0,
      "end_time": 712856.0,
      "text": "When a firm dies, some people will lose their jobs."
    },
    {
      "index": 202,
      "start_time": 712880.0,
      "end_time": 715256.0,
      "text": "And others will lose their money."
    },
    {
      "index": 203,
      "start_time": 715280.0,
      "end_time": 718696.0,
      "text": "And in the case of social and green enterprises,"
    },
    {
      "index": 204,
      "start_time": 718720.0,
      "end_time": 722976.0,
      "text": "the death of this business can have a negative impact"
    },
    {
      "index": 205,
      "start_time": 723000.0,
      "end_time": 726440.0,
      "text": "on the ecosystems or communities they were trying to serve."
    },
    {
      "index": 206,
      "start_time": 727360.0,
      "end_time": 731456.0,
      "text": "But what does it mean to fail mindfully?"
    },
    {
      "index": 207,
      "start_time": 731480.0,
      "end_time": 736216.0,
      "text": "It means being aware of the impact, of the consequences"
    },
    {
      "index": 208,
      "start_time": 736240.0,
      "end_time": 738120.0,
      "text": "of the failure of that business."
    },
    {
      "index": 209,
      "start_time": 738920.0,
      "end_time": 741439.0,
      "text": "Being aware of the lessons learned."
    },
    {
      "index": 210,
      "start_time": 741960.0,
      "end_time": 745456.0,
      "text": "And being aware of the responsibility"
    },
    {
      "index": 211,
      "start_time": 745480.0,
      "end_time": 747680.0,
      "text": "to share those learnings with the world."
    },
    {
      "index": 212,
      "start_time": 748400.0,
      "end_time": 749616.0,
      "text": "Thank you."
    },
    {
      "index": 213,
      "start_time": 749640.0,
      "end_time": 753800.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    }
  ]
}